    "v0.1.0": {
      "created_at": "2026-03-29T11:45:40Z",
      "description": "Vagrant Story Client + AP World v0.1.0,\r\nIt's been months of work, but I think it's finally ready for the collective hivemind to give it a bash outside of our main troupe of merry man. \r\n\r\nHuge and heartfelt thanks to @ToxicFrog, @gobolt , @Chaotic Brave Alisdair, @Stroll  and of course @ArsonAssassin for his fantastic library.\r\n\r\nDefault locations are Boss Kills, Chests, Break Arts and Chain/Defence skills. \r\n\r\nThe Goal is to kill the dark angel in the final encounter in the game.\r\n\r\nOptions,\r\nMore locations to add:\r\nInclude Prologue to add a few checks,\r\nInclude New Game Plus,\r\nRoomSanity for going into every room at least one,\r\nPanelSanity for each trap in the game,\r\nInclude Time Trial,\r\n\r\nProgression Options:\r\nVanilla will allow you to start from the beginning of the game,\r\nOpen will allow you to start from one of the workshops in the game,\r\n\r\nItem Drop Options:\r\nVanilla will provide all of the items from the base game as you play through,\r\nHeavy will provide all possible items from the base. Also provides a limit.,\r\nChest Drop Choices,\r\nBoss Drop Choices,\r\n\r\nSkill Unlock Options:\r\nSet how many chains needed for chain ability unlocks, or just leave it vanilla,\r\nSet how many kills needed for break art unlocks, or just leave it vanilla,\r\n\r\nTeleporting:\r\nProvide teleport as always on in case of issues or have a teleport item added to the pool!,\r\nSet teleport to have 0 mp cost,\r\nSet all teleport locations to be available at the start!,\r\n\r\nKnown Issues:\r\nPuzzle rooms in the yaml don't work yet.,\r\nOpen world is easilly winnable with teleport, mcguffins to be added,\r\nSome items still being served despite the logic not requiring them. (gold key, rood inverse etc),\r\nWine Cellar might still trigger with open world at the start. Timing issue.",
      "download_url": "https://github.com/riezahughes/VagrantStoryAPWorld/releases/download/v0.1.0/vagrantstory.apworld",
      "has_manifest": true,
      "hash_sha256": "d119711c678f621cc4c903de25e5c418a101e5b09a7eb12cf8a845bef49cc98c",
      "html_url": "https://github.com/riezahughes/VagrantStoryAPWorld/releases/tag/v0.1.0",
      "minimum_ap_version": "0.6.5",
